# https://w3id.org/dqvch#accessibility
<https://w3id.org/dqvch#accessibility> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/dqvch#accessibility> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dqv#Dimension> .
<https://w3id.org/dqvch#accessibility> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Accessibility refers to additional information that govern access to data."@en .
<https://w3id.org/dqvch#accessibility> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#narrower> <https://w3id.org/dqvch#availability> .
<https://w3id.org/dqvch#accessibility> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#narrower> <https://w3id.org/dqvch#confidentiality> .
<https://w3id.org/dqvch#accessibility> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#narrower> <https://w3id.org/dqvch#integrity> .
<https://w3id.org/dqvch#accessibility> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Accessibility"@en .
<https://w3id.org/dqvch#accessibility> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dqv#inCategory> <https://w3id.org/dqvch#contextualDimensions> .
