<https://w3id.org/dqvch#relevance> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#hadPrimarySource> <https://www.dama-nl.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3DQ-Dictionary-of-Dimensions-of-Data-Quality-version-1.2-d.d.-14-Nov-2020.pdf> .
