# https://w3id.org/dqvch#understandability
<https://w3id.org/dqvch#understandability> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/dqvch#understandability> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dqv#Dimension> .
<https://w3id.org/dqvch#understandability> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Understandability refers to the ease with which data can be comprehended and processed by users, including both humans and tools."@en .
<https://w3id.org/dqvch#understandability> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#narrower> <https://w3id.org/dqvch#appropriateness> .
